text: Jacob van Geuns (15 November 1872 - 12 November 1952) was a Dutch fencer. He competed in the individual épée event at the 1912 Summer Olympics. ==References== Category:1872 births Category:1952 deaths Category:Dutch male fencers Category:Olympic fencers of the Netherlands Category:Fencers at the 1912 Summer Olympics Category:Sportspeople from Utrecht (city)
